title: #329 LIVE From Moontower w/ Chris Distefano & Ron Bennington
description:
Hey hey Tuesgay's, we're wishing you a happy holidays with our live episode from the 2017 Moontower Comedy Festival with guests Christ Distefano and Ron Bennington. Enjoy!

Sponsored by: Native Deodorant (nativedeodorant.com code: tuesdays) & Cannae Pro Gear (cannaeprogear.com code: tuesdays)
